### Getting booking details (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/customerSupportAgent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "2",
  "userMessage": "Hi, when does my booking begin?"
}

### Cancelling booking (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/customerSupportAgent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "2",
  "userMessage": "Please cancel my booking MS-569, my name is jon heny."
}

### Upload image with text (multipart) - use curl or IntelliJ HTTP Client
POST http://localhost:8080/customerSupportAgent/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sessionId"

3
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userMessage"

帮我把这张票退了
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="ticket.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./src/test/resources/test-image.png
--boundary--